  "text": "Prometheus metric naming convention enforcement in prometheus/prometheus repository:\n\n1. **model/labels/labels_common.go (IsValid method)** - Lines 117-132\n   - Validates both metric names and label names using ValidationScheme\n   - Calls validationScheme.IsValidMetricName() for metric name validation (line 123)\n   - Calls validationScheme.IsValidLabelName() for label name validation (line 127)\n   - Used throughout the codebase for comprehensive label validation\n\n2. **model/textparse/protobufparse.go** - Lines 447-455\n   - Validates metric names during protobuf parsing\n   - Uses model.UTF8Validation.IsValidMetricName() to validate metric names (line 451)\n   - Validates help text presence and UTF-8 validity (line 454)\n   - Returns error if metric name or help text is invalid\n\n3. **model/textparse/openmetricsparse.go** - Lines 512-527\n   - Validates help text UTF-8 validity during OpenMetrics parsing (line 512)\n   - Enforces unit suffix naming convention (lines 525-527)\n   - Ensures unit is a proper suffix of the metric name with underscore separator\n\n4. **model/rulefmt/rulefmt.go** - Lines 240-280\n   - Validates recording rule names using IsValidMetricName (line 247)\n   - Validates label names using IsValidLabelName (line 264)\n   - Validates annotation names using IsValidLabelName (line 278)\n   - Provides comprehensive rule group validation with the nameValidationScheme parameter\n\n5. **storage/remote/codec.go (validateLabelsAndMetricName function)** - Lines 850-866\n   - Validates metric and label names in remote read operations\n   - Uses model.UTF8Validation.IsValidMetricName() for metric validation (line 854)\n   - Uses model.UTF8Validation.IsValidLabelName() for label validation (line 857)\n   - Checks for duplicate label names (line 863)\n\n6. **model/relabel/relabel.go** - Line 168\n   - Validates target label names in relabeling configuration\n   - Uses c.NameValidationScheme.IsValidLabelName() for validation\n   - Enforces label naming conventions during relabel action validation\n\nThe ValidationScheme type and its methods (IsValidMetricName, IsValidLabelName) are defined in the external github.com/prometheus/common/model package, supporting both LegacyValidation (strict ASCII/snake_case rules) and UTF8Validation (UTF-8 only requirement) modes."
}

